# Đề xuất: Khắc phục Chapter cụt lủn

## Pattern từ kịch bản tham khảo (11 chapters, 149-196 words)

Phân tích cấu trúc tất cả chapters tham khảo, mỗi chapter có **3 BEATS**:

### BEAT 1: SCENE (hành động cụ thể)
Nơi chốn → nhân vật hành động → hậu quả tức thì

### BEAT 2: CONTEXT (đặt sự kiện vào thế giới)  
Thân phận, vị trí, kẻ thù, hoàn cảnh — trả lời "tại sao điều này quan trọng?"

### BEAT 3: STAKES / FORESHADOW (mở ra mối đe dọa)
Câu cuối luôn chỉ về **tương lai** hoặc **mối đe dọa lớn hơn** — không bao giờ dừng ở scene.

---

## Minh chứng từ TỪNG chapter:

### Ch1 (149w) — Leprosy discovery
| Beat | Content |
|---|---|
| SCENE | Courtyard → boys scratch arm → you don't feel → tutor candle test → white face |
| CONTEXT | "You're a prince of Jerusalem. Father is king. Stone palace. Enemies on every side." |
| STAKES | **"Something is growing inside your body. Something that will eat you alive."** |

### Ch3 (162w) — Coronation
| Beat | Content |
|---|---|
| SCENE | Father dies → crown passes → barons kneel → some calculating |
| CONTEXT | "Kingdom = thin strip between Mediterranean and sea of enemies" |
| STAKES | **"Saladin wants Jerusalem back. And you, a 13-year-old leper, are the only thing standing in his way."** |

### Ch4 (196w) — Montgisard
| Beat | Content |
|---|---|
| SCENE | Saladin 26,000 men → you have 375 → charge → devastation → Saladin escapes |
| CONTEXT | "A hero. The entire kingdom erupts. A leper boy defeated the greatest general." |
| STAKES | **"For one single night, you forget the clock is ticking."** |

### Ch5 (190w) — Rotting throne
| Beat | Content |
|---|---|
| SCENE | Hand useless → skin cracking → court factions → French knight |
| CONTEXT | "4 months ago, you drove Saladin into the desert. Tonight, your own court is the battlefield." |
| STAKES | **"He has something better. Time. And you're running out of it."** |

### Ch7 (186w) — Last ride
| Beat | Content |
|---|---|
| SCENE | Saladin sieges fortress → you order litter to front → army rallies → Saladin withdraws |
| CONTEXT | "They've seen kings ride into battle. They've never seen one carried." |
| STAKES | **"This is the last time you will ever see a battlefield."** |

---

## Bản mới viết (ch1, 244w) — thiếu Beat 2 và Beat 3

| Beat | Content |
|---|---|
| SCENE | Courtyard → nail game → blood → no pain → tutor freezes → color drains |
| CONTEXT | ❌ THIẾU (có mention father/mother nhưng ở ĐẦU, không phải sau scene) |
| STAKES | ❌ THIẾU — kết bằng "Your right arm is already dead." → observation, không forward |

Kết quả: chapter cảm giác **chỉ kể xong 1 việc rồi dừng**, không mở ra thế giới hay mối đe dọa.

---

## Đề xuất sửa

Thêm vào **write prompt** (section CONTENT DEVELOPMENT → CHAPTER FLOW), principle mới:

```
CHAPTER COMPLETENESS — 3 BEATS:
Every chapter must contain all 3 beats (not necessarily in this order):

  BEAT 1 — SCENE: The main_key_data event, told through action.
  BEAT 2 — CONTEXT: Why this event matters — position in the world, 
           who is watching, what is at stake. 
           (1-3 sentences placing the event in the larger picture)
  BEAT 3 — FORWARD TENSION: The last 1-3 sentences must point BEYOND 
           this chapter — a threat growing, a clock ticking, 
           a consequence that hasn't arrived yet.

  A chapter with only SCENE = observation report (cụt lủn)
  A chapter with SCENE + CONTEXT = documentary segment (flat)
  A chapter with SCENE + CONTEXT + FORWARD TENSION = lived experience (complete)

  FORWARD TENSION examples:
    ✓ "Something is growing inside your body. Something that will eat you alive."
    ✓ "He has something better. Time. And you're running out of it."
    ✓ "This is the last time you will ever see a battlefield."
    ✗ "Your right arm is already dead." (observation — no forward)
    ✗ "William releases your hand." (action — no stakes)
```

### Lưu ý quan trọng:
- Principle này **không mâu thuẫn** với closing_type (cold_fact, paradox, weight, forward_pull)
  - closing_type = **HOW** to phrase the ending
  - 3-beat rule = **WHAT** the ending must contain (forward tension)
- **Không hardcode** word count cho từng beat
- **Không áp đặt** thứ tự beat — chỉ yêu cầu cả 3 phải có mặt
